{"type":"message","id":"6d5868a6","parentId":"de82942d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:41:10.027Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_cnfrvfi074qh_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4688\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2788\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation proposed] the\n[master f62a59a] pulse: 2026-03-23 204042\n 7 files changed, 315 insertions(+), 104 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 204042.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 204042.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 203040.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 204042 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next priority, but I need a working implementation first. I should create a script that can analyze pulse logs for invariant patterns and test the compression-causal duality hypothesis.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tidy-nexus","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4688\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2788\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation proposed] the\n[master f62a59a] pulse: 2026-03-23 204042\n 7 files changed, 315 insertions(+), 104 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 204042.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 204042.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 203040.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 204042 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next priority, but I need a working implementation first. I should create a script that can analyze pulse logs for invariant patterns and test the compression-causal duality hypothesis.\n","name":"powershell Bypass"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774312870024}}
